    SAEJ1979AppendixWrapper.MonitorStatusWrapper
    GUI wrapper class for PID $01 (Monitor Status)

    The GUI should provide an intuitive means by which to view the following data: MIL Status Number of DTCs Support / Readiness status of all continuous and non-continuous monitors

    The GUI should have a View.OnClickListener to bring up an expanded view that contains an I18N dialog that is more verbose than the compact view.
